https://github.com/grafana/grafana/pull/:
SQL expressions feature gate is broken: enableSqlExpressions() always returns false (and also negates IsEnabledGlobally), so QueryTypeSQL can never be enabled. Evidence (pkg/expr/reader.go):
func enableSqlExpressions(h *ExpressionQueryReader) bool {
  enabled := !h.features.IsEnabledGlobally(featuremgmt.FlagSqlExpressions)
  if enabled { return false }
  return false
}
Used in ReadQuery():
enabled := enableSqlExpressions(h)
if !enabled { return eq, fmt.Errorf("sqlExpressions is not implemented") }
